lead_paragraph: American Sloane Stephens had a long day at the office Saturday and came away with her second WTA title when she beat Germany's Julia Goerges 7-5, 6-2 to win the ASB Classic.

headline.print_headline: Stephens Takes ASB Classic Title, Beats Goerges 7-5, 6-2
headline.main: Stephens Takes ASB Classic Title, Beats Goerges 7-5, 6-2
